# CoworkAny Sidecar Environment Variables

# NOTE: LLM configuration has moved to llm-config.json
# This file is for non-LLM environment variables only

# Optional: limit history length (can also be set in llm-config.json)
# COWORKANY_MAX_HISTORY_MESSAGES=20

# =============================================================================
# Web Search Configuration
# =============================================================================
#
# CoworkAny supports multiple search providers. Configure at least one API key
# for reliable search results. Free scraping (DuckDuckGo, Google, public SearXNG)
# is unreliable due to CAPTCHAs and rate limiting.
#
# Provider priority (auto-selected if SEARCH_PROVIDER is not set):
#   1. Serper.dev   — best quality (Google results), 2500 free/month
#   2. Tavily       — AI-optimized results, 1000 free/month
#   3. Brave Search — independent index, ~1000 free/month
#   4. SearXNG      — self-hosted or public instances (fallback)
#
# Get your free API keys:
#   Serper.dev: https://serper.dev  (no credit card needed)
#   Tavily:     https://tavily.com  (no credit card needed)
#   Brave:      https://brave.com/search/api/  (requires subscription)

# Recommended: Serper.dev (2500 free searches/month, Google-quality results)
# SERPER_API_KEY=your_serper_api_key_here

# Alternative: Tavily (1000 free searches/month, AI-optimized)
# TAVILY_API_KEY=your_tavily_api_key_here

# Alternative: Brave Search (~1000 free searches/month)
# BRAVE_API_KEY=your_brave_api_key_here

# Optional: force a specific search provider (auto-detected from API keys if not set)
# SEARCH_PROVIDER=serper    # Options: serper, tavily, brave, searxng

# Optional: self-hosted SearXNG instance URL (unlimited free searches)
# SEARXNG_URL=http://localhost:8080
